        <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-primary-light">Is Sharp Tabs free to use?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
                Yes! Sharp Tabs is completely free with all features included. The only premium feature is AI-powered
