                your own Gemini API key in the settings.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-primary-light">
                What's the difference between Free & Premium?
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
                All features are free - themes, custom CSS, backgrounds, workspaces, session backups, tab suspending,
                and all customization options. Premium only adds AI features (AI Grouping, AI Group Naming, AI Cleanup)
                which use Gemini API. You can also use your own Gemini API key to access AI features for free.
                <br />
                Please consider supporting Sharp Tabs by purchasing a premium plan so we can continue to improve the extension.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
